OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy morning, with
OL,6,Fsome light rain in places, notably in
OL,7,Fthe east. The cloud may break during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon to allow some sunshine
OL,9,Fthrough. Feeling a little milder.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy overnight with further
OL,12,Foutbreaks of patchy rain and drizzle,
OL,13,Fhowever some heavier bursts are likely
OL,14,Fto develop and move northwards later
OL,15,Fin the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
